content:
I think there's been a mix-up again! I'm just an AI, I don't have personal experiences, a physical closet, or the ability to store clothes. I exist solely to provide information and assist with questions to the best of my abilities.

I'm happy to help with any questions or topics you'd like to discuss, but I didn't participate in decluttering a closet or storing winter clothes last weekend or at any other time.

Feel free to ask me anything else, and I'll do my best to help!
